0:02:46.720,0:02:50.300
Sometimes I went against my wish to do them,

0:02:50.300,0:02:57.040
but after doing those things I would feel so guilty for doing them and tomorrow I would still do them again.

0:02:57.040,0:02:58.260
Things like...

0:02:58.260,0:03:05.840
At the age 10-12 years I had a group of friends, living in the same neighbourhood.

0:03:05.840,0:03:11.140
... things like stealing little things from the people in the community.

0:03:11.140,0:03:15.760
I started from stealing money from my mothers handbag and using it...

0:03:15.760,0:03:19.420
At the end of the day, when asked, I would deny stealing it.

0:03:19.420,0:03:24.300
It went on like that for so many years.

0:03:24.300,0:03:27.820
When I was growing up, I noticed that something was wrong,

0:03:27.820,0:03:33.160
but I couldn't "fish out" what really was happening.

0:03:33.160,0:03:36.020
In 2006 I lost my mother.

0:03:36.020,0:03:41.420
After the burial, my mum's sister called a family meeting,

0:03:41.420,0:03:45.700
saying that there was something that they wanted to tell me.

0:03:45.700,0:03:47.500
I asked what it was.

0:03:47.500,0:03:53.280
They told me that when I was born...

0:03:53.280,0:04:01.400
From the first day I was delivered here on earth, I cried continually for 7 days.

0:04:01.400,0:04:09.880
My mother had no option but to take me to her father, who happened to be a very strong native doctor.

0:04:09.880,0:04:14.000
He never wore anything on his feet until when he died.

0:04:14.000,0:04:18.240
Every thing in his compound was a shrine - he was as strong as that.

0:04:18.240,0:04:24.140
Nevertheless, he wasn't able to find solution, so he went to another bigger witch doctor.

0:04:24.140,0:04:31.800
They consulted the witch doctor and he said that he was the one who came back as an incarnation,

0:04:31.800,0:04:36.200
that he wasn't supposed to be alive, that he was supposed to die before he came back.

0:04:36.200,0:04:38.620
But there's was nothing the man could have done.

0:04:38.620,0:04:44.340
They asked what they could do - he said that either they leave me to die,

0:04:44.340,0:04:49.160
or they go and buy things mentioned to them.

0:04:49.160,0:04:53.540
They were told to go to 3 junctions and perform some sacrifices, by 12 am.

0:04:53.540,0:04:55.340
After the sacrifice...

0:04:55.340,0:04:59.100
The man would die for me to live.

0:04:59.100,0:05:02.140
It was a very big problem in the house.

0:05:02.140,0:05:03.440
They went back home.

0:05:03.440,0:05:09.440
The father of my mother had so many wives but he loved my mum, as his first daughter.

0:05:09.440,0:05:11.660
He never wanted to disappoint my mum.

0:05:11.660,0:05:16.500
One day he called a meeting and said that he is going to do the sacrifice.

0:05:16.500,0:05:19.940
They asked him what would happen after the sacrifice.

0:05:19.940,0:05:27.940
He told them that they should keep me behind; when I grow up I would continue where he stopped.

0:05:27.940,0:05:34.500
So, they went and purchased the items mentioned to them by the "bigger" witch-doctor they went to.

0:05:34.500,0:05:38.760
By 12 am the sacrifice was conducted

0:05:38.760,0:05:41.680
After few days the man died.

0:05:41.680,0:05:46.100
That is how I stopped crying.

0:05:46.100,0:05:49.320
The story did not make sense to me,

0:05:49.320,0:05:51.900
I asked why was the story coming then?

0:05:51.900,0:05:55.600
Why didn't it come before, when my mother was alive?

0:05:55.600,0:06:01.200
The woman told me that she was the only woman who was living with my mum at that time.

0:06:01.200,0:06:04.600
She knew everything that happened.

0:06:04.600,0:06:08.180
But later the woman repented; she was the deaconess in the Assembly of God church.

0:06:08.180,0:06:10.120
My mum also repented.

0:06:10.120,0:06:12.440
However they Ignored the idol.

0:06:12.440,0:06:17.840
I never knew, all this years, that the idol was living in me and walking in me.

0:06:17.840,0:06:20.580
As the time went by, I was growing up and the story didn't mean anything to me.

0:06:20.580,0:06:24.980
I started hanging out with my old friends.

0:06:24.980,0:06:31.480
Some of those friends grown up to be mature, having their own gangs.

0:06:31.480,0:06:36.820
Sometimes they could call me and we would go to people houses and burgle them,

0:06:36.820,0:06:39.300
and take them away; sometimes we took money from them.

0:06:39.300,0:06:42.160
One strange thing always happened.

0:06:42.160,0:06:50.840
If I kept looking at a glass cup on the desk and I would be imagining that glass cup will fall down and break;

0:06:50.880,0:06:55.780
I would be imagining for 4 or 5 minutes, then and you would see that glass cup fall down and break.

0:06:55.780,0:07:04.680
If anybody offended me, they must have had a big problem, leading to accident, or...

0:07:04.680,0:07:07.160
You must get yourself in a very big problem.

0:07:07.160,0:07:09.740
I was very proud of it.

0:07:09.740,0:07:13.120
During those days, I made a lot of money.

0:07:13.120,0:07:18.080
I was using big cars, I made money; the money was coming.

0:07:18.080,0:07:24.600
You made us to understand that it was immediately after the death of the father of your mother,

0:07:24.600,0:07:27.160
when this spirit fully possessed you.

0:07:27.160,0:07:28.720
- Is that correct?
- Yes.

0:07:28.720,0:07:31.980
- You were said to be his incarnation?
- Yes.

0:07:31.980,0:07:34.620
- And he was a notorious witch doctor during his time?
- Yes.

0:07:34.620,0:07:36.280
It goes this way:

0:07:36.280,0:07:38.520
If you have a mission to carry out...

0:07:38.520,0:07:42.360
We thought that we were very smart and intelligent.

0:07:42.360,0:07:47.080
We would go to a witch doctor for a consultation

0:07:47.080,0:07:50.220
During the consultation we were called to look in the mirror,

0:07:50.220,0:07:54.380
and the witch doctor would tell you if you would make it or not.

0:07:54.380,0:07:57.780
He would tell you if you are going to succeed or not.

0:07:57.780,0:08:02.660
If there was a problem, you would have to fortify yourself before the journey.

0:08:02.660,0:08:10.860
When we entered the house, I didn't need to ask where the money was; I knew it.

0:08:10.860,0:08:12.680
I would go straight where the money was and I would pick it.

0:08:12.680,0:08:15.920
That is how it was working for me.

0:08:15.920,0:08:26.120
In 2010, I noticed a problem - a growth that became bigger at daily basis.

0:08:26.120,0:08:38.120
Another time I noticed other growth on my hip; this one was growing bigger than the first one.

0:08:38.120,0:08:40.040
So I hid it to myself; I didn't want to tell anybody.

0:08:40.040,0:08:42.880
I started going to hospitals.

0:08:42.880,0:08:48.280
There is no hospital in Nigeria that I did not go to.

0:08:48.280,0:08:50.700
I went to witch-doctors.

0:08:50.700,0:08:52.920
I went to prayer houses.

0:08:52.920,0:08:59.280
I went to many churches, which I don't want to call names - many churches.

0:08:59.280,0:09:05.220
I didn't want to die, because all these years I thought I was careful not to lose my life.

0:09:05.220,0:09:08.340
But this sickness came.

0:09:08.340,0:09:11.340
I would have gone to any place, no matter the cost.

0:09:11.340,0:09:16.860
There was a place, where I told a man, "If my health was going to cost a human head - tell me."

0:09:16.860,0:09:17.840
I was ready.

0:09:17.840,0:09:25.780
When the health issue stepped in, I started selling things because all my money was gone.

0:09:25.780,0:09:35.260
As there was no solution, I started selling my properties, cars, but at end of the day nothing happened.

0:09:35.260,0:09:40.740
The person that bought my last car asked me, "Why can't you go to the Synagogue?"

0:09:40.740,0:09:42.620
I said, "Stop telling me that."

0:09:42.620,0:09:51.720
