0:11:31.160,0:11:34.000
So, I was staying in the hotel.

0:11:34.000,0:11:38.080
When all my hope was lost, I called one of my brothers, a friend.

0:11:38.080,0:11:43.460
I told him,  "Young man I've seen my death. I know that I am going to die but before I die,

0:11:43.460,0:11:46.080
look at how my burial would happen."

0:11:46.080,0:11:51.860
After that conversation with him, I began to scatter things in the room.

0:11:51.860,0:11:55.760
Somebody that was inside with me said that I should cool down I would not die.

0:11:55.760,0:12:00.540
In the meantime, the television went off in my hotel room.

0:12:00.540,0:12:05.640
Somebody was trying to fix it I found Emmanuel TV.

0:12:05.640,0:12:10.780
When Emmanuel TV was on...

0:12:10.780,0:12:16.740
I began to watch, I saw testimonies, healing and many things.

0:12:16.740,0:12:23.860
I wondered if this was the same man that they said things about.

0:12:23.860,0:12:26.140
Yet, I had not been convinced.

0:12:26.140,0:12:32.760
At the end of the day, I said to myself, "I went to herbal homes, prayer-houses,  churches;

0:12:32.760,0:12:33.940
let me also go there."

0:12:33.940,0:12:38.500
I came only to try, like I tried in other places before.

0:12:38.500,0:12:41.920
When I came to the gate, a voice spoke to me to go back.

0:12:41.920,0:12:46.800
I went back to my hotel.

0:12:46.800,0:12:50.740
A friend advised me to go to India.

0:12:50.740,0:12:56.860
I went to India; this was my first time I was in India...

0:12:56.860,0:12:59.800
This is a medical visa.

0:12:59.800,0:13:02.300
I went and came back, I want to max hospital

0:13:02.300,0:13:05.400
and I spent three months nothing happened.

0:13:05.400,0:13:09.380
I came back, I went back to another hospital in India,

0:13:09.380,0:13:11.240
I spent three months there and I came back.

0:13:11.240,0:13:19.260
I went back there again to "Action Cancer" hospital in New Delhi, in India.

0:13:19.260,0:13:24.500
When I came back, they asked me to come back to SCOAN, since I already was in India.

0:13:24.500,0:13:28.540
The last time I was in India, the doctor asked me, "Who did I come with?"

0:13:28.540,0:13:30.640
I said, I hadn't come with anybody.

0:13:30.640,0:13:31.740
He left.

0:13:31.740,0:13:35.440
There was a young man I met in the flat while I was going; he had somebody there...

0:13:35.440,0:13:36.640
I told him, "Look, where I'm going".

0:13:36.640,0:13:37.800
I gave him my number.

0:13:37.800,0:13:43.340
After few days, the person who received my number called me and they located me.

0:13:43.340,0:13:47.180
The man said that since there was nobody with me, he wanted to assist me.

0:13:47.180,0:13:52.100
He took me to the "Action cancer" hospital, where I was before.

0:13:52.100,0:14:06.020
During my first medical check-up, the doctor shook his head, and he was a senior doctor.

0:14:06.020,0:14:10.700
He shook his head and asked me to go, and the man who was with me stayed with the doctor.

0:14:10.700,0:14:12.740
When the man came out, he was sweating.

0:14:12.740,0:14:14.160
I asked him what happened.

0:14:14.160,0:14:20.080
He said that I needed some relative to sign medical documents,

0:14:20.080,0:14:24.500
and he couldn't do it because he didn't know me, and anything could happen.

0:14:24.500,0:14:30.640
He began to tell me the stories of people who came from Nigeria with cancer and died.

0:14:30.640,0:14:32.700
My mind was troubled.

0:14:32.700,0:14:35.220
I asked him to go with me back to the doctor.

0:14:35.220,0:14:42.980
Doctor told me that he was giving me only 25% of chances.

0:14:42.980,0:14:48.280
Before, I heard that doctors would give 50/50 of chances, but in my case they gave only 25%.

0:14:48.280,0:14:54.100
I asked why they gave me so low chances.

0:14:54.100,0:14:55.320
I was scared.

0:14:55.320,0:15:02.520
I came back to Nigeria and I received Morning Water and I went home.

